<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="27" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[264,1324,283,590]" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,433,363,389]" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was originally described using a large series from San Gerónimo, Purula, Coban, and Cubilguitz from Vera Paz, 
<collectingCountry box="[894,1025,404,430]" name="Guatemala" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
. The specimens studied from 
<collectingCountry box="[328,442,444,470]" name="Honduras" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Honduras</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[500,620,444,470]" name="Nicaragua" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Nicaragua</collectingCountry>
do not exhibit any major differences when compared to the Guatemalan specimens. The new records in 
<collectingCountry box="[793,913,484,510]" name="Nicaragua" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Nicaragua</collectingCountry>
extend the distribution 
<quantity box="[1200,1290,484,510]" metricMagnitude="5" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.6" pageId="4" pageNumber="27" unit="km" value="260.0">260 km</quantity>
to the southeast of Coban, 
<collectingCountry box="[553,680,524,550]" name="Guatemala" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
across several chains of mountains in 
<collectingCountry box="[1145,1272,524,550]" name="Guatemala" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[264,382,564,590]" name="Honduras" pageId="4" pageNumber="27">Honduras</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
